cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.IT, cs.DS 

The paper deals with the application of neural networks for spatio-temporal forecasting of taxi demand-supply. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves the use of GPS data and spatial partitioning techniques, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
